+/// supplied, bypassing the hard-reject contract. (An impossible MONTH like
+/// `2025-13-01`, and impossible TIMES like `25:00:00` / `:60` / `:61`, already
+/// NULL out; only impossible DAYS roll over — that is the sole residue.)
